{"id":427295,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/02/王左中右-春节临近，北京朝阳区的气氛略紧张/","date":"2016-02-02T11:43:13Z","modified":"2016-02-02T11:43:13Z","title":"王左中右 | 春节临近，北京朝阳区的气氛略紧张","content":"<p>赵大妈观察冲锋衣男已经两天了。</p>\n<p>绣花胡同口的老槐树下，王老太手里的针线活不停，一条喜庆的红围巾就快完工。</p>\n<p>下午2点的阳光温暖出奇，赵大妈刚要上前打招呼，她的面前走过一个人，那个神秘的冲锋衣男。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.38.26.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.38.26\" width=\"573\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427297\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.38.26.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.38.26-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>王老太将毛线缠在钢针上，头也不抬地说</p>\n<p>“赵大妈啊，刘四在澳大利亚带孙子，黄李在西城陪儿子，我门口晒着的千张你拿回家煮吧。”</p>\n<p>水龙头哗哗声响，千张被扔进了淘米水里，渐渐显示出三行字：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.40.54.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.40.54\" width=\"289\" height=\"190\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427298\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.40.54.png 289w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.40.54-230x150.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 289px) 100vw, 289px\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.40.47.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.40.47\" width=\"288\" height=\"190\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427299\" /></p>\n<p>10秒后字消失。</p>\n<p>赵大妈眉头紧锁，回忆起下午的脚步声。</p>\n<p><strong> “身高185cm，结合鞋子和小路间摩擦声分贝，体重75kg~80kg。”</strong></p>\n<p>两天前，冲锋衣突然搬进刘四家的二楼，一般敢于租在朝阳区的人大抵是没有问题的。但为什么这个外地人春节期间入住？一般外地人这个时候都已离开北京回老家过年。</p>\n<p>后续情报显示，冲锋衣行踪诡异，曾在朝阳多个小区出现，且分布在各个时间段。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.42.01.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.42.01\" width=\"570\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.42.01.png 570w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.42.01-300x188.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" /></p>\n<p>冲锋衣的闽南口音更让赵大妈联想到2016年初一些新的国际形势，这更加深了她的警惕。</p>\n<p>首都的平安容不得一粒来路不明的沙子。想到这，赵大妈提起菜刀用力剁下去，鱼身一分为二。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.42.42.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.42.42\" width=\"572\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.42.42.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.42.42-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>朝阳区大概有384万人，但称的上CYQZ的并不多。5年前，刚办完退休手续的赵大妈以为这辈子就这样糊弄过去了，却在当晚接到一个陌生的电话。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.43.21.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.43.21\" width=\"572\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427302\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.43.21.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.43.21-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>电话里的人字正腔圆，像极每晚7点的新闻联播。此后，赵大妈成为一名光荣的CYQZ。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.43.47.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.43.47\" width=\"573\" height=\"358\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427303\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.43.47.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.43.47-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>叮铃铃，赵大妈等待的那个电话终于响起。</p>\n<p>每次通话，都以接头暗号开始。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.44.17.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.44.17\" width=\"572\" height=\"355\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427304\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.44.17.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.44.17-300x186.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>“今天烧了些啥菜？”</p>\n<p>意思是今天有什么情况。</p>\n<p>“除夕人少，跑了不少小区，才买到鱼。”</p>\n<p>意思是冲锋衣出现在不少小区。</p>\n<p>电话那头的人迟疑了一会，说：</p>\n<p><strong>“盐不要放了，多放点油。”</strong></p>\n<p>翻译过来就是其他人不用查了，盯住这个人。</p>\n<p>“做鱼汤我最拿手了。”</p>\n<p>除夕，晚上8点。</p>\n<p>整个北京城灯火璀璨，每一个窗户射出的灯光都显得温暖幸福。勤劳的中国人辛辛苦苦一年，就是为了这个时候跟家人坐在一起吃个年夜饭，看个春晚。</p>\n<p>但越是这种时刻，危险系数就越高。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.45.19.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.45.19\" width=\"573\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.45.19.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.45.19-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>赵大妈朝窗外望去，刘四家二楼亮着灯。过了10分钟，漆黑一片。</p>\n<p>“这人竟然不看春晚。”</p>\n<p>在确认对方没有出门后，赵大妈拿起望远镜观察对方。10分钟后，冲锋衣走到阳台接电话。赵大妈死死盯着男子嘴部的动作，大脑飞速的运转着，唇语翻译：</p>\n<p>东。西。在。我。这。儿。今。天……</p>\n<p>冲锋衣转头看了眼这边。</p>\n<p>“有杀气！ ”赵大妈果断趴下。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.46.18.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.46.18\" width=\"572\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427306\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.46.18.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.46.18-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>砰的一声，冲锋衣出门了。</p>\n<p>东西是什么？</p>\n<p>为什么要在除夕交？</p>\n<p>赵大妈顾不及多想，赶紧冲出去。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.46.57.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.46.57\" width=\"286\" height=\"177\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427307\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.47.16.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.47.16\" width=\"290\" height=\"177\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427308\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.47.16.png 290w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.47.16-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>“新年好”</strong></p>\n<p>迎面而来的冲锋衣压低帽子，声音低沉，匆匆地离开。</p>\n<p>赵大妈发现他的身后背着一个大包。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.49.05.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.49.05\" width=\"572\" height=\"358\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.49.05.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.49.05-300x188.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>王老太不知什么时候站在了赵大妈的身后：</p>\n<p>“苍北小区的杨麻婆，昨儿买了一条大鱼，够吃1个月。那个朵儿胡同的胡秃子，你还记得？傍晚还遛狗，真是爱狗如命。”</p>\n<p>长期的群众工作，使得CYQZ有一套很隐蔽的暗语。</p>\n<p>大鱼=情报上传</p>\n<p>遛狗=收集情报</p>\n<p>这些暗语隐藏在生活用语中，有轻微的音高差异，常人难以发觉。</p>\n<p>杨麻婆，苍北小区广场舞领队。听到这个人的名字，赵大妈不禁咬下嘴唇，握紧拳头。如果目光可以点燃物体，眼前的老槐树早已化成灰烬。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.49.58.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.49.58\" width=\"573\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.49.58.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.49.58-300x186.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>在其他小区大放异彩的2015年，柯震西屋祖名尹照杰毛丁先后被查。但绣花胡同能接触到的名人很少，成绩惨淡。年末CYQZ总结会上，小区代表云集。部长雪莉按成绩重新划分广场舞阵地。绣花胡同丢掉了唯一一块跳舞面积，被苍北小区夺走。</p>\n<p>想到这，赵大妈就一阵胸闷。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.50.40.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.50.40\" width=\"573\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427311\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.50.40.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.50.40-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>她愤懑地走到赵四家门口，左腿一个发力——Duang—— 垃圾桶应声倒地。</p>\n<p>谁知这时垃圾桶里吐出一张被揉烂的地图，准确的说是朝阳西广营的地图。</p>\n<p>很显然，这一带都是老北京，根本不会用地图，这个地图只可能是冲锋衣的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.51.18.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.51.18\" width=\"573\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.51.18.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.51.18-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>地图被耐心地铺开，西广营的各小区方位都在赵大妈大脑里重绘。</p>\n<p>这里是幸福路花园路，这边是农民体育馆……</p>\n<p>苍南胡同多了个红色圆珠笔标注的三角形记号</p>\n<p>赵大妈心喜：“就是这了！”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.51.48.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.51.48\" width=\"288\" height=\"176\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.51.48.png 288w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.51.48-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.52.03.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.52.03\" width=\"288\" height=\"178\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.52.03.png 288w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.52.03-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.52.10.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.52.10\" width=\"288\" height=\"177\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427315\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.52.10.png 288w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.52.10-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\" /></p>\n<p>晚上9点，苍南胡同。</p>\n<p>竹斜街上，行人寥寥。</p>\n<p>胡同深处飘来喜悦祥和的春晚歌舞声。</p>\n<p>冷风如刀割，赵大妈脸颊惨红却目光如炬。</p>\n<p>远远地跟在冲锋衣身后。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.53.10.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.53.10\" width=\"572\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427316\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.53.10.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.53.10-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>突然冲锋衣猛一回头，随后脚步声突然加快。</p>\n<p>这一下把赵大妈吓了一个踉跄，出门太急赵大妈还穿着那件紫色羽绒服，金棕色缎面提花鞋。赵大妈带着懊恼继续追了上去。<br />\n这时，她发现冲锋衣跑进了百里巷。</p>\n<p>赵大妈窃喜，她在百里巷度过了童年，巷子有多少块砖头砖头上有多少划痕她都了如指掌。百里巷只有一个出口。她抄小路守住出口，冲锋衣果然稳稳地落在了她的视野内。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.54.01.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.54.01\" width=\"570\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.54.01.png 570w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.54.01-300x188.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" /></p>\n<p>咚咚咚</p>\n<p>冲锋衣敲着一户人家的门</p>\n<p>一个戴眼镜的女人探出头来</p>\n<p>门前灯昏沉地亮着</p>\n<p>赵大妈的心猛烈的跳动着</p>\n<p>她的耳朵已听不到春晚的歌舞声</p>\n<p>她的牙齿用力的咬住舌头</p>\n<p>她的左手狠狠的压着胸口</p>\n<p>她的眼睛死死地盯着冲锋衣嘴部的动作</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.54.43.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.54.43\" width=\"572\" height=\"355\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427318\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.54.43.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.54.43-300x186.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>冲锋衣开口了。</p>\n<p>唇语翻译的结果一字一字的在赵大妈的脑海呈现，等她们串成一句话时，赵大妈突然瘫倒在地。</p>\n<p>冲锋衣说的是</p>\n<p>京东年欢惠，<br />\n春节不打烊。<br />\n您刚买的年货到了！</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.56.49.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-02-02 at 上午3.56.49\" width=\"510\" height=\"293\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427319\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.56.49.png 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/Screen-Shot-2016-02-02-at-上午3.56.49-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\" /></p>\n","author":996,"categories":[9203],"tags":[24191,27293,28380,28933]}